                  </persName>
            ; from whence he sent Layton with the Physic, who deliver'd it. In the mean Time, a Woman enquiring for Blewit, the Prosecuor's Maid brought her to him at the Ale-house, and left the Key with him; he and the Woman went in together, and shut the Maid out, they staid about half an Hour, and then came out again, and he went to the Ale-house where Layton came to him; when the Prosecutor came Home about 9 at Night, he found that his House had been rob'd. Layton confest, that he and Blewit finding a Ladder, got over the Wall into the Yard, and the Door being open they took away the Goods. Blewit was <rs id="t17251208-57-verdict278" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17251208-57-verdict278" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
